en.appendTitle: Append a new field with type 'auto' after this field (Ctrl+Shift+Ins)
en.appendSubmenuTitle: Select the type of the field to be appended
en.appendTitleAuto: Append a new field with type 'auto' (Ctrl+Shift+Ins)
en.actionsMenu: Click to open the actions menu (Ctrl+M)
en.expandTitle:
Click to expand/collapse this field (Ctrl+E). 
 Ctrl+Click to expand/collapse including all childs.
en.insertTitle: Insert a new field with type 'auto' before this field (Ctrl+Ins)
en.insertSub: Select the type of the field to be inserted
en.typeTitle: Change the type of this field
en.openUrl: Ctrl+Click or Ctrl+Enter to open url in new window
en.validationCannotMove: Cannot move a field into a child of itself
en.autoType: Field type "auto". The field type is automatically determined from the value and can be a string, number, boolean, or null.
en.objectType: Field type "object". An object contains an unordered set of key/value pairs.
en.arrayType: Field type "array". An array contains an ordered collection of values.
en.stringType: Field type "string". Field type is not determined from the value, but always returned as string.
